list.formulaSource:
package it.custom.pd.compiledformula

import it.custom.alc.mathlibrary.service._
import scala.collection.mutable.Map
import java.time._

class TCM_A00011 { 

	private var mathematicalLibrary = new MathematicalLibrary
	private var matrixLibrary = new MatrixLibrary
	private var stringLibrary = new StringLibrary
	private var dateLibrary = new DateLibrary
	private var actuarialLibrary = new ActuarialLibrary
	private var tableLibrary = new TableLibrary
	private var typeConversionLibrary = new TypeConversion

	def execute(systemFields: Map[String, Any], internalFields: Map[String, Any], ruleFields: Map[String, Map[String, Any]]) = { 

		var AL = 0d
		var BE = 0d
		var GA = 0d
		var HA = 0d
		var eta = 0d
		AL = 0d
		BE = 0d
		GA = 0d
		HA = 0d
		eta = 0d
		eta = dateLibrary.betweenInYears(systemFields.get("DT_NASCITA").get.asInstanceOf[LocalDate])
		AL = 0.09d
		BE = 0d
		GA = 0.008d
		HA = AL+BE+GA
		systemFields.put("PURO_RIF",actuarialLibrary.temporaryAnnuityDeath(eta.toInt,systemFields.get("N").get.asInstanceOf[Double].toInt,internalFields.get("T_T").get.asInstanceOf[Double],internalFields.get("UNIX_02").get.asInstanceOf[Array[Array[Double]]]))
		systemFields.put("P_TAR",systemFields.get("PURO_RIF").get.asInstanceOf[Double]/( 1d-HA ))
		systemFields.put("P_TAR",mathematicalLibrary.round(systemFields.get("PURO_RIF").get.asInstanceOf[Double],4d.toInt))
		systemFields.put("P_TAR",systemFields.get("P_TAR").get.asInstanceOf[Double]*systemFields.get("CAP").get.asInstanceOf[Double])

	}

}
